    "A Power BI reporting layer connected directly to the HubSpot data model, respecting its actual relationships.",
    'Custom measures and dashboards for the specific views leadership wanted, refreshing automatically.',
    "Delivered across a 12-hour time-zone gap and a tight timeline, running discovery in the client's late morning (our late evening), then shipping overnight work that landed by the client's next morning.",
  ]}
  outcome="An exceptional outcome, in Deanna's own words. The complex HubSpot project shipped on time despite the 12-hour gap. Leadership got the single reporting view they came for."
  quote="Duten Nexa is instrumental in delivering high-quality Power BI reporting for a complex HubSpot project within a tight time frame. Their aptitude, diligence, and problem-solving skills enabled us to seamlessly navigate challenges, despite a 12-hour time difference, and achieve an exceptional outcome. We highly recommend Duten Nexa for their expertise, perseverance, and commitment to excellence."
